                I am pleased to inform you that you have been offered provisional admission into the Department of
                <span class="font-weight-bold px-10px border-bottom-bold"> @Model.Department.Name.ToUpper() </span> in the Faculty of <span class="font-weight-bold px-10px border-bottom-bold"> @Model.Department.Faculty.Name.ToUpper() </span>
