                <li class="list-mb">The Associate Certificate Programme is non-residential; therefore the University will not provide accomodation for its students in the programme.</li>
                <li class="list-mb">Regulations concerning fees and other matters will be made from time to time and will be binding on all students.</li>
            </ol>

            <p>Congratulations and accept our best wishes for a successful stay in the University.</p>

